Ms. Marie  Adler-KravecasMost recently served as president and founder of Wellconnected, a consumer direct marketing company for affordable personalized gift items. Previously was with Myron Corp., an international business-to-business direct marketing company where she was instrumental in opening the company's manufacturing plants in the United Kingdom and China. 2009 Second QuarterAdded to: Systemax Inc. - Port Washington, NYSystemax sells personal computers, computer supplies and accessories, consumer electronics, and industrial products. Revenues are $3 billion.















 















 

















