Insider Activity


Individual




Marie Adler-Kravecas



Ms. Marie Adler-Kravecas is Independent Director at Systemax, Inc. and a Member at Young Presidents' Organization, Inc. She is on the Board of Directors at Systemax, Inc. and Children's Aid & Family Services, Inc.
Ms. Adler-Kravecas was previously employed as Founder by Wellconnected LLC, President by Wellconnected LLC, and President by Myron Corp.
She received her undergraduate degree from George Washington University.



